              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Interactive Exhibits: The exhibits at Wonderfood Museum are replicated with the utmost detail and are sure to tempt your appetite."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Wonderfood Museum is a fun place to see and photograph larger-than-life models of Malaysia's national obsession - food, in all its varied and delicious forms. If you have ever seen those ultra-realistic plastic  replicas of dishes outside Japanese restaurants you will know what to expect here except that the models are mostly of Malaysian food and they are huge. The museum showcases Malaysia's unique food culture, drawn from the nation's rich multi-racial diversity. The replicas are beautifully made and if you weren't hungry when you entered the museum you will be by the time you leave."
              }
            ]
          }
